version number: 0.0.1

Overview
--------

Chatbot Entities Extractor.

Installation / Usage
--------------------

To install use pip:

    $ pip install chatbotentities


Or clone the repo:

    $ git clone https://github.com/kverdecia/chatbotentities.git
    $ python setup.py install
